<p>
  <span class="nym">Brightnod</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*berhtaz</i> + <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*naudiz</i> 'need, necessity'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  


